== Ottoman-German Alliance ==
It is debatable whether it was Ottoman Empire or Germany that attacked Russia. The battleships were nominally Ottoman vessels, but their crews were German, and the motives of the attack are at best hazy.--[[User:Eleman|Eleman]] ([[User talk:Eleman|talk]]) 08:27, 10 March 2011 (UTC)
